- `\disc(L)` not `\disc L`
- `\Aut(G)` not `\Aut G`
- `\End(V)` not `\End V`
- `\Hom(A,B)` not `\Hom A,B`

#### Tensor Products
- Use `\tensor` (not `\otimes`)
- Use `\Tensor` (not `\bigotimes`)

